<item>
            <title>[LU-12259] conf-sanity test 50h fails with  &#8216;tunefs OST1 failed&#8217;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12259</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity test_50h fails with  &#8216;tunefs OST1 failed&#8217;. Most of the failures of this test with this error message are for PPC.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the suite_log for a recent failure,  &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b1449c50-668f-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b1449c50-668f-11e9-8bb1-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;, the output from test 50h is &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== conf-sanity test 50h: LU-642: activate deactivated OST ============================================ 09:14:47 (1556010887)
CMD: trevis-55vm11 tunefs.lustre --param osc.active=0 /dev/mapper/ost1_flakey
checking for existing Lustre data: found
Reading CONFIGS/mountdata

   Read previous values:
Target:     lustre-OST0000
Index:      0
Lustre FS:  lustre
Mount type: ldiskfs
Flags:      0x2
              (OST )
Persistent mount opts: ,errors=remount-ro
Parameters: mgsnode=10.9.3.116@tcp sys.timeout=20


   Permanent disk data:
Target:     lustre-OST0000
Index:      0
Lustre FS:  lustre
Mount type: ldiskfs
Flags:      0x42
              (OST update )
Persistent mount opts: ,errors=remount-ro
Parameters: mgsnode=10.9.3.116@tcp sys.timeout=20 osc.active=0

 conf-sanity test_50h: @@@@@@ FAIL: tunefs OST1 failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the OSS console log, we can see the tunefs command&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[14155.015811] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == conf-sanity test 50h: LU-642: activate deactivated OST ============================================ 09:14:47 (1556010887)
[14155.186811] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: tunefs.lustre --param osc.active=0 /dev/mapper/ost1_flakey
[14155.607766] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  conf-sanity test_50h: @@@@@@ FAIL: tunefs OST1 failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For this test, there are no errors in any of the node console and dmesg logs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for other failures are at&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5477d70c-3b11-11e9-8f69-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5477d70c-3b11-11e9-8f69-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/062b5864-bd06-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/062b5864-bd06-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
